ector.js","line":89},{"title":"../../../src/engine/scheduleAdapter.js","target":"../../../src/engine/scheduleAdapter.js","line":90},{"title":"../../../src/engine/coachContext.js","target":"../../../src/engine/coachContext.js","line":91},{"title":"../../../src/ui/screens/aparateLipsa.js","target":"../../../src/ui/screens/aparateLipsa.js","line":92},{"title":"../../../06-sessions-log/HANDOVER_GLOBAL_2026-04-30_evening","target":"../../../06-sessions-log/HANDOVER_GLOBAL_2026-04-30_evening","line":93},{"title":"../../../📥_inbox/HANDOVER_2026-05-13_chat_acasa_post_s2_landed_strategic_findings","target":"../../../📥_inbox/HANDOVER_2026-05-13_chat_acasa_post_s2_landed_strategic_findings","line":94},{"title":"../../../📤_outbox/LATEST","target":"../../../📤_outbox/LATEST","line":95},{"title":"../../../📤_outbox/_archive/2026-05/448_LATEST_PREVIOUS_WIKI_INGEST_2026_05_13_CALENDAR_V1_S1_TO_S1_7_CONSUMED","target":"../../../📤_outbox/_archive/2026-05/448_LATEST_PREVIOUS_WIKI_INGEST_2026_05_13_CALENDAR_V1_S1_TO_S1_7_CONSUMED","line":96}],"metadata":{"title":"Engine Coach Director — Orchestrator Central Pipeline §42.10","type":"entity-engine","status":"landed","last_updated":"2026-05-13e","cross_refs":["[[../adrs/adr-026-offline-coaching-tree]]","[[../adrs/adr-024-goal-driven-program-templates]]","[[../adrs/adr-030-adapter-design-pattern]]","[[../adrs/adr-020-storage-tiering-strategy]]","[[../../concepts/calendar-feature-v1-spec]]","[[../../03-decisions/DECISION_LOG]] §2026-05-11 STAGE 4 SUB-BATCH 2","[[../../../src/engine/coachDirector.js]]"],"amendments":[{"date":"2026-05-13","note":"buildSession() S2 path forward consume wv2-missing-equipment localStorage filter (Calendar V1 S1.7 LANDED missing equipment lifecycle) — pre-build filtrează exerciții care folosesc aparate marcate lipsa din lista, propune alternative parity equipment-swap logic fără user input. Multi-week constraint propagate Engine"},{"date":"2026-05-13b","note":"S2 Production Wiring LANDED chain 3 atomic commits clean (S2.A `7c2f520` scheduleAdapter UI-side adapter + S2.B `fce846a` coachContext integrate aparate-lipsa filter + calendar override + S2.C `a77587c` aparateLipsa.js page port + state.currentScreen enum extend) — Adapt + execute Co-CTO tactical decision Daniel verbatim *\"asta e decizia ta nu a mea\"* post CC pre-flight grep detected slip §AR.20 candidate spec PROMPT_CC referenced `goalAdaptation.recomputeWeekSchedule()` procedural method add violating ADR 026 §9 pure-function engines invariant. Option 1 reinterpret S2 plan UI-side adapter + buildCoachContext extend + engines UNCHANGED. ZERO engine module mutation. Engine pipeline §42.10 8 prescriptive engines pure-function discipline preserved invariant. `buildCoachContext()` extend prin `safeCtx.meta` defensive-read pattern absorb `wv2-missing-equipment` filter Tier 0 localStorage + `ctx.meta.calendarOverride` mid-week edit ephemeral propagate Big 6 invariant downstream Engine"},{"date":"2026-05-13e","note":"Bundle 4 workout-preview port + per-exercise refusal flow + mid-session augmentation LANDED `429c189` single atomic commit clean Bugatti single-concern — orchestrator-level behavior augmentation ONLY (NU engine mutation ADR 026 §9 pure-function engines invariant preserved invariant). Engine pipeline §42.10 8 prescriptive engines + 3 methods NEW STAGE 4 SUB-BATCH 2 (`buildLightMobility` + `rebalanceWeekAfterSkip` + `generateSafeSessionForRestDay`) preserved invariant unchanged. `buildCoachContext()` extend prin `safeCtx.meta` defensive-read pattern absorb refusal counter `wv2-refusal-counter` + skipped exercises `wv2-skipped-exercises` Tier 0 localStorage (per ADR 020 §1.4 Tier 0 parity pattern) → cascade alternative exhaustion mechanism downstream Engine"},{"date":"2026-05-13c","note":"S3 Guards Bundle 1 LANDED chain 2 atomic commits clean (S3.C `d41e111` session guard double-start + S3.D `47729ed` bottom-nav HIDE in-session) — orchestrator-level session lifecycle behavior change ONLY (NU engine mutation). `body.in-session` body class toggle UI-side per ADR 026 §9 pure-function engines invariant preserved + ADR 030 D2 thin scope adapter pattern. Engine pipeline §42.10 8 prescriptive engines + 3 methods NEW STAGE 4 SUB-BATCH 2 (`buildLightMobility` + `rebalanceWeekAfterSkip` + `generateSafeSessionForRestDay`) preserved invariant unchanged. `buildSession()` orchestrator flow `startSession()` entry point modificat doar pentru double-start guard `state.sessActive + state.sessStart` check BEFORE draft detection logic + zero prompt redirect Gigel-smooth + body.in-session class toggle session lifecycle entry/exit + nav hide. Tests 2984 → 3006 PASS (+22 net new) vitest cluster `session-guard-double-start.test.js` +10 + `session-bottom-nav-hide.test.js` +12. ZERO engine module mutation. Draft recovery `confirm()` prompt PRESERVED INTACT distinction (separate concern sesiune crashed previous). EXIT paths cancelWorkout + closeSummary (NOT endSession — rating modal still in-session UX, nav reappear deferred). Post §AR.20 quadruple violation halt v1 PROMPT_CC + §AR.21 codification origin CC autonomous Opus + redo spec v2 grep evidence verbatim inline per file/function referenced + first-attempt validation effective §AR.21 enforcement post-codification ZERO slip surfaced"}]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"key":"wiki/entities/engines/engine-coach-director.md"},
